{"tid":1035714,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有啲人真係好「度縮」","createTime":"2019-02-24T18:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T12:33:19.000Z","uid":82917,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"57d61c895bc17e81c1a0085855540736b03dd6c2","tid":1035714,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T18:52:51.000Z","msg":"啱啱落堂同個同學去食飯，其實約左大半個月先約得成咁當然滿心期待啦！我地就分開去嘅，走個陣我就順路車埋佢返屋企，路上條友突然急尿咪擺佢去target放水，返到嚟見佢揸住兩支水笑笑口仲以為佢買嚟慰勞我咁sweet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌拿星！完全係我自作多情！條撚屌夠膽死問我拎返$1.5，仲要開口話連埋tax架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴線我又無叫你買水俾我，我車你返去又無見我問你收油錢？寒酸到呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已經第二次，是咪我個額頭刻撚住「水魚」兩隻字？？"},{"pid":"c0510508034e3a3ec31884bc45ffbe973b26e71a","tid":1035714,"uid":25857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T18:57:50.000Z","msg":"你又搵ford水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591a613af44bbb7928b8ca0e5637ec363a7f6e25","tid":1035714,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0510508034e3a3ec31884bc45ffbe973b26e71a","tid":1035714,"uid":25857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T18:57:50.000Z","msg":"你又搵ford水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T18:58:34.000Z","msg":"衰撚過ford呀！呢單係佢自作多情 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"395713459e6ce99531454fe87b0fdc14b1f758b0","tid":1035714,"uid":25857,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"591a613af44bbb7928b8ca0e5637ec363a7f6e25","tid":1035714,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote